data.description: Enchanting 5-bdrm, 4-bthrm Crystal Falls home! Nestled in this vibrant community offering perfect blend of serenity & convenience. High walkability quick access to delightful parks and trails, surrounded by array of commuting options & plethora of shopping choices, from charming independent eateries to convenient big-box retailers. First floor a masterpiece of design w/ primary bedroom and bathroom suite & separate soaking tub & ample shower plus massive walk-in closet, extra storage - a tranquil escape after a long workday! A second full bedroom and bathroom on the main floor ideal for guests, creating a multi-generational living space, accommodating demanding workdays. Heart of this home is the kitchen w/ massive island anchoring open floor-plan, seamless interaction w/ living area. Kitchen overlooks backyard & spacious covered patio, thoughtfully incorporated w/original construction. Whether hosting gatherings, enjoying morning coffee, or creating lasting memories w/ family, this space is a true gem. Custom & thoughtful adaptations further elevate this home; 'French attached' wood mantle adorns gas fireplace. Venturing to the second level, 3 addit’l bedrms + spacious living/family room catering to your entertainment desires of hosting movies, playing games, setting up a ping pong or billiard table for endless fun. Storage solutions are thoughtfully integrated throughout the home, ensuring you have ample space for all your belongings. Delightful 'nook' below the staircase adds character & ‘fun options’. Designed w/ ease of maintenance in mind limited carpet stairs only, making cleaning a breeze! Upgraded paint, well-planned exterior walkways. Hobbyists and those with electric vehicles will appreciate the garage equipped with 220 electrical. Don't miss this opportunity to call this remarkable home yours. Crystal Falls offers not just a residence, but a lifestyle filled with comfort, style, & vibrant community.
